# React-BurgerApp #
Simple App developed with React front-end framework and Firebase Database instance as the Backend

## Build: ##

- create project with create-react-app: create-react-app <NAME_OF_YOUR_PROJECT> --scripts-version 1.1.5
- eject project and add css modules with: npm run eject (edited in webpack_config_dev & webpack_config_prod)

## Set-up & add external libraries: ##

* npm install
* npm install --save prop-types
* npm install --save axios
* npm install --save react-router react-router-dom

## Start the server ##

npm start
